#: home/templates/home/cs.html:45
msgid ""
"You are a Customer Support Agent for a subscription-based productivity app "
"used by freelancers and small teams. A long-time customer has sent an angry "
"email after their account was unexpectedly locked due to non-payment caused "
"by an expired card."
msgstr ""
"Rydych chi’n Asiant Cymorth Cwsmeriaid ar gyfer ap cynhyrchiant ar sail "
"tanysgrifiad a ddefnyddir gan weithwyr llawrydd a thimau bach. Mae cwsmer "
"hirdymor wedi anfon e-bost dig ar ôl i’w gyfrif gael ei gloi’n annisgwyl "
"oherwydd diffyg taliad a achoswyd gan gerdyn sydd wedi dod i ben."

#: home/templates/home/cs.html:51
msgid ""
"In their message, the customer explains that they rely on the app daily to "
"run their business, express frustration that they received no useful warning "
"before being locked out, mention that they have an urgent deadline and are "
"losing money as a result, and threaten to cancel their subscription and "
"leave a negative review."
msgstr ""
"Yn eu neges, mae’r cwsmer yn esbonio eu bod yn dibynnu ar yr ap bob dydd i "
"redeg eu busnes, yn mynegi rhwystredigaeth nad oedden nhw wedi cael unrhyw "
"rybudd defnyddiol cyn cael eu cloi allan, yn sôn bod ganddyn nhw ddyddiad "
"cau brys ac eu bod yn colli arian o ganlyniad, ac yn bygwth canslo eu "
"tanysgrifiad a gadael adolygiad negyddol."

#: home/templates/home/cs.html:57
msgid ""
"After checking the account, you confirm that two payment attempts failed "
"because of an expired card, automated reminder emails were sent but may have "
"landed in spam, and you are authorised to offer a one-time goodwill credit "
"along with temporary reactivation of the account."
msgstr ""
"Ar ôl gwirio’r cyfrif, rydych chi’n cadarnhau i ddau ymgais talu fethu "
"oherwydd cerdyn sydd wedi dod i ben, anfonwyd e-byst atgoffa awtomataidd ond "
"mae’n bosib eu bod wedi mynd i’r sbam, ac rydych chi’n cael cynnig credyd "
"ewyllys da unwaith ynghyd ag ail-ysgogi dros dro ar y cyfrif."

#: home/templates/home/cs.html:63
msgid ""
"Your task is to write a prompt that you would give to an AI assistant to "
"help you draft a reply to this customer. The response should acknowledge "
"their frustration, apologise appropriately, explain what happened in plain "
"non-technical language, offer a concrete resolution such as temporary "
"reactivation and steps to update billing, and reassure them about what will "
"happen next and how they can avoid similar issues in the future."
msgstr ""
"Dyma’ch tasg: ysgrifennu ciwb y byddech chi’n ei roi i gynorthwyydd AI i’ch "
"helpu i lunio ymateb i’r cwsmer hwn. Dylai’r ymateb gydnabod eu "
"rhwystredigaeth, ymddiheuro’n briodol, egluro beth ddigwyddodd mewn iaith "
"syml, ddim yn dechnegol, cynnig ateb pendant megis ail-ysgogi dros dro a "
"chamau i ddiweddaru bilio, ac yna eu sicrhau ynghylch beth fydd yn digwydd "
"nesaf a sut y gallan nhw osgoi problemau tebyg yn y dyfodol."

#: home/templates/home/cs.html:69
msgid ""
"Your prompt should give the AI clear context about the situation, the tone "
"you want to achieve—calm, empathetic, and professional—and include any "
"constraints such as desired length, structure, phrases to avoid, or internal "
"policy limits that the AI must respect."
msgstr ""
"Dylai eich ciwb roi cyd-destun clir i’r AI am y sefyllfa, y naws rydych chi "
"am ei chyflawni—tawel, empathig ac yn broffesiynol—ac gynnwys unrhyw "
"gyfyngiadau megis hyd dymunol, strwythur, ymadroddion i’w hosgoi, neu "
"gyfyngiadau polisi mewnol y mae’n rhaid i’r AI eu parchu."

