#: home/templates/home/cw.html:41
msgid ""
"You are a Copywriter for a small but growing SaaS company that helps "
"freelancers and agencies manage their clients, proposals, and invoices in "
"one place. The team is about to launch a new Client Portal feature."
msgstr ""
"Rydych chi’n Gopïwr ar gyfer cwmni SaaS bach sy’n tyfu ac sy’n helpu "
"gweithwyr llawrydd ac asiantaethau i reoli eu cleientiaid, eu cynnig "
"cynigion a’u hanfonebau i gyd mewn un lle. Mae’r tîm ar fin lansio nodwedd "
"Portal Cleient newydd."

#: home/templates/home/cw.html:47
msgid ""
"The Client Portal allows customers to share project timelines, files, and "
"updates in one secure space, enable clients to approve proposals and sign "
"documents online, reduce back-and-forth email threads and missed "
"attachments, and give clients a single place to see what’s happening next."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r Portal Cleient yn caniatáu i gwsmeriaid rannu llinellau amser "
"prosiect, ffeiliau a diweddariadau mewn un gofod diogel; galluogi "
"cleientiaid i gymeradwyo cynigion ac arwyddo dogfennau ar-lein; lleihau "
"edafedd e-byst yn ôl ac ymlaen a ffeiliau cysylltiedig a gollwyd; ac yn rhoi "
"un lle clir i gleientiaid weld beth sy’n dod nesaf."

#: home/templates/home/cw.html:53
msgid ""
"You need to brief an AI assistant to help you draft both a launch email for "
"existing customers announcing the Client Portal and the key sections of a "
"landing page, including the headline, subheading, benefits, and call to "
"action."
msgstr ""
"Mae angen i chi friffio cynorthwyydd AI i’ch helpu i lunio e-bost lansio ar "
"gyfer cwsmeriaid presennol yn cyhoeddi’r Portal Cleient, ynghyd â phrif "
"adrannau tudalen lanio gan gynnwys y pennawd, yr is-bennawd, y manteision "
"a’r alwad i weithredu."

#: home/templates/home/cw.html:59
msgid ""
"The audience is time-poor freelancers and small agencies who juggle multiple "
"clients and dislike admin. The tone should be clear, energetic, and "
"reassuring, emphasising saving time, reducing chaos, and helping them appear "
"more professional to their clients."
msgstr ""
"Y gynulleidfa yw gweithwyr llawrydd a chwmnïau bach sy’n brin o amser, yn "
"rheoli nifer o gleientiaid ac yn casáu gwaith papur. Dylai’r naws fod yn "
"glir, egniol ac yn dawelgar—yn pwysleisio arbed amser, lleihau anhrefn ac eu "
"helpu i ymddangos yn fwy proffesiynol i’w cleientiaid."

#: home/templates/home/cw.html:65
msgid ""
"Your task is to write a prompt that you would give to the AI assistant to "
"generate this email and landing page copy. Your prompt should include clear "
"context about the product and audience, the goals of the campaign, and "
"constraints such as tone of voice, structure, word count ranges, and any "
"phrases or clichés to avoid."
msgstr ""
"Eich tasg yw ysgrifennu ciwb y byddech yn ei roi i’r cynorthwyydd AI i "
"gynhyrchu’r e-bost a’r copi tudalen lanio. Dylai’ch ciwb gynnwys cyd-destun "
"clir am y cynnyrch a’r gynulleidfa, nodau’r ymgyrch, a chyfyngiadau megis "
"naws yr iaith, strwythur, ystod hyd geiriau, ac unrhyw ymadroddion neu "
"glisheu i’w hosgoi."

#: home/templates/home/cw.html:71
