#: home/templates/home/da.html:45
msgid ""
"You are a Data Analyst at a growing SaaS company that provides a web "
"platform for small businesses. Each month you produce a Product Usage and "
"Adoption Dashboard that tracks how actively customers are engaging with key "
"features."
msgstr ""
"Rydych chi’n Ddadansoddwr Data mewn cwmni SaaS sy’n tyfu ac sy’n darparu "
"platfform gwe i fusnesau bach. Bob mis rydych chi’n cynhyrchu Dangosiad "
"Defnydd a Mabwysiadu Cynnyrch sy’n olrhain pa mor weithgar mae cwsmeriaid yn "
"ymgysylltu â nodweddion allweddol."

#: home/templates/home/da.html:51
msgid ""
"This month’s dashboard highlights several notable patterns. Overall logins "
"have increased, but one of the core product features has experienced a clear "
"and meaningful drop in usage. New customers appear to be adopting key "
"features more quickly than long-term customers, and churn risk is rising "
"within a particular customer segment. Additionally, a recent UX change seems "
"to have altered behaviour across two major user flows."
msgstr ""
"Mae dangosiad mis hwn yn tynnu sylw at sawl patrwm nodedig. Mae "
"mewngofnodion cyffredinol wedi cynyddu, ond mae un nodwedd graidd wedi gweld "
"gostyngiad amlwg yn ei defnydd. Mae cwsmeriaid newydd yn ymddangos yn fwy "
"cyflym i fabwysiadu nodweddion allweddol na chwsmeriaid tymor hir, ac mae’r "
"risg chwalu’n cynyddu mewn un segment penodol. Yn ogystal, mae newid "
"diweddar yn y profiad defnyddiwr wedi newid ymddygiad ar draws dwy llif "
"ddefnyddwyr."

#: home/templates/home/da.html:57
msgid ""
"Your task is to send a summary update to the leadership team and product "
"managers. In this update you should explain what trends you observe in the "
"data, why these trends matter for the business, and what potential "
"decisions, risks, or follow-up questions emerge from the patterns you have "
"identified."
msgstr ""
"Eich tasg yw anfon crynodeb at y tîm arweinyddiaeth a’r rheolwyr cynnyrch. "
"Dylech egluro pa dueddiadau sy’n ymddangos yn y data, pam eu bod yn bwysig i "
"’r busnes, a pha benderfyniadau, risgiau neu gwestiynau dilynol sy’n codi "
"o’r patrymau hynny."

#: home/templates/home/da.html:63
msgid ""
"Write a prompt that you would give to an AI assistant to help you draft this "
"summary. Your prompt should include clear context about the dashboard, the "
"intended audience of non-technical leaders, and specific instructions about "
"the structure of the summary, such as highlighting key insights, explaining "
"the impact, and suggesting recommended next steps."
msgstr ""
"Ysgrifennwch giwb y byddech yn ei roi i gynorthwyydd AI i’ch helpu i lunio’r "
"crynodeb hwn. Dylai’ch ciwb gynnwys cyd-destun clir am y dangosiad, y "
"gynulleidfa darged o arweinwyr annechnegol, ac yn ogystal cyfarwyddiadau "
"penodol ar strwythur y crynodeb, gan gynnwys prif fewnwelediadau, effaith, a "
"chamau nesaf argymelledig."

#: home/templates/home/da.html:69
msgid ""
"Hint: Imagine you are briefing a consultant who has never seen your product "
