#: home/templates/home/it.html:46
msgid ""
"You are an IT Specialist at a mid-sized organisation with around 250 staff "
"working both in the office and remotely. Your team is preparing to roll out "
"a major system upgrade that affects the company’s core tools, including "
"email, file storage, and VPN access."
msgstr ""
"Rydych chi’n Arbenigwr TG mewn sefydliad canolig ei faint gyda thua 250 o "
"staff yn gweithio yn y swyddfa ac o bell. Mae eich tîm yn paratoi i gyflwyno "
"uwchraddiad system mawr sy’n effeithio ar brif offer y cwmni, gan gynnwys e-"
"bost, storio ffeiliau a mynediad VPN."

#: home/templates/home/it.html:52
msgid ""
"The upcoming upgrade introduces several important improvements. Users will "
"benefit from enhanced security through mandatory two-factor authentication, "
"along with a cleaner and faster webmail interface. File storage and sharing "
"rules will be updated to improve consistency and safety across the "
"organisation. In addition, there will be short periods of planned downtime "
"over a single weekend to complete the upgrade safely."
msgstr ""
"Bydd yr uwchraddiad yn cyflwyno sawl gwelliant pwysig. Bydd defnyddwyr yn "
"elwa ar ddiogelwch uwch drwy ddilysu dau gam gorfodol, ynghyd ag wyneb we e-"
"bost glanach a chyflymach. Bydd y rheolau ar gyfer storio a rhannu "
"ffeiliau’n cael eu diweddaru i wella cysondeb a diogelwch ar draws y "
"sefydliad. Yn ogystal, bydd cyfnodau byr o ddiffodd wedi’u cynllunio dros un "
"penwythnos i gwblhau’r uwchraddiad yn ddiogel."

#: home/templates/home/it.html:58
msgid ""
"You are aware that many of your colleagues are not technical and may feel "
"overwhelmed by system changes. Some may ignore long or complicated emails, "
"and others may miss critical instructions unless the information is "
"presented in a clear, structured, and approachable way."
msgstr ""
"Rydych yn ymwybodol nad yw llawer o’ch cydweithwyr yn dechnegol ac efallai y "
"byddan nhw’n teimlo’n llethu gan newidiadau system. Gall rhai anwybyddu e-"
"byst hir neu gymhleth, ac eraill fethu cyfarwyddiadau pwysig oni bai bod yr "
"wybodaeth yn cael ei chyflwyno mewn ffordd glir, strwythuredig ac hawdd ei "
"dilyn."

#: home/templates/home/it.html:64
msgid ""
"Your task is to send an internal announcement that explains what is changing "
"and why the upgrade is happening now. The message should highlight the main "
"benefits in plain, accessible language, clearly outline the key dates and "
"expected downtime, guide staff through any required actions such as setting "
"up two-factor authentication, and direct them to the appropriate place for "
"help or training."
msgstr ""
"Eich tasg yw anfon cyhoeddiad mewnol sy’n egluro beth sy’n newid a pham "
"mae’r uwchraddiad yn digwydd nawr. Dylai’r neges amlygu’r prif fanteision "
"mewn iaith syml a hygyrch, nodi’r dyddiadau allweddol a’r diffodd "
"disgwyliedig, tywys staff drwy unrhyw gamau angenrheidiol megis gosod dilysu "
"dau gam, ac yna eu cyfeirio at y lle iawn am gymorth neu hyfforddiant."

#: home/templates/home/it.html:70
msgid ""
"You want to use an AI assistant to help draft this announcement. Your goal "
"is to write a prompt that gives the AI enough information to produce a "
"clear, accurate, and reassuring message for colleagues with mixed levels of "
"technical confidence."
msgstr ""
"Rydych eisiau defnyddio cynorthwyydd AI i helpu llunio’r cyhoeddiad hwn. "
"Eich nod yw ysgrifennu ciwb sy’n rhoi digon o wybodaeth i’r AI greu neges "
"glir, gywir ac atyniadol i gydweithwyr ag amryw lefelau o hyder technegol."

#: home/templates/home/it.html:76
msgid ""
"Your prompt should include context about the organisation and the tools "
"being upgraded, details about the audience, and constraints such as the "
"desired tone—calm, supportive, and not alarmist—along with guidance on "
"length and any specific policies, requirements, or wording the AI should "
"follow or avoid."
msgstr ""
"Dylai eich ciwb gynnwys cyd-destun am y sefydliad a’r offer sy’n cael eu "
"huwchraddio, manylion am y gynulleidfa, a chyfyngiadau megis naws y neges—"
"dawel, cefnogol, ac nid yn banigol—ynghyd â chanllawiau ar hyd y neges ac "
"unrhyw bolisïau neu eiriad penodol y dylai’r AI ei ddilyn neu ei osgoi."

#: home/templates/home/it.html:82
msgid ""
"Hint: Imagine you are briefing a helpdesk engineer to write the announcement "
