#: home/templates/home/ms.html:52
msgid ""
"In four weeks, you are running a launch campaign aimed at a mix of "
"audiences. These include existing customers who may upgrade or expand their "
"usage, new prospects who are currently comparing your tool with competing "
"platforms, and partners or resellers who need a clear and compelling story "
"to communicate to their clients."
