#: home/templates/home/ms.html:58
msgid ""
"You want to use an AI assistant to help outline the campaign. You will need "
"ideas for the key value propositions and messaging angles that should "
"resonate with each audience group, recommendations on which channels to use "
"such as email, social posts, in-app messages, webinars, or landing pages, a "
"simple timeline covering the four weeks leading up to the launch, and "
"example content pieces such as subject lines, hooks, social copy, or webinar "
"titles."
